TIC TAC TOE PROJECT
● Given Below is the python code for the tic tac toe game
● This game consists of two types of mode
○ The single player mode(against the computer)
○ The multiplayer mode (2 players)
● The layout of the tic tac toe table has been made in the orthodox style
,however for interaction, the player has to give an integer as an input which
corresponds to the position where he wants to mark
● While playing in single player mode the player will get two options,which are
they can play as player 1 or as player two
● After the code the output(from the terminal) is also given
